.TH WIKIPEDIA "1" "December 2025" "wikipedia 202208181946-git" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
wikipedia \- Lookup something on Wikipedia
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B wikipedia
[\fI\,OPTIONS\/\fR] [\fI\,QUERY\/\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B wikipedia
is a script for looking up articles on Wikipedia from the terminal. It retrieves article summaries and information using the Wikipedia API.
.PP
The script provides quick access to Wikipedia content without leaving the terminal.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-\-help
Display help message with usage information and available options
.TP
.BR \-\-config
Generate or regenerate user configuration file with default settings
.TP
.BR \-\-version
Show script version information and exit
.TP
.BR \-\-options
Display all available command-line options
.TP
.BR \-\-debug
Enable debug mode with verbose output and command tracing (set -x)
.TP
.BR \-\-raw
Disable colorized output for plain text display
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
.B wikipedia "Linux kernel"
Search for Linux kernel article
.TP
.B wikipedia bash
Search for bash article
.SH FILES
.TP
.B ~/.config/myscripts/wikipedia/settings.conf
User configuration file for wikipedia preferences
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Success
.TP
.B 1
General error or article not found
.TP
.B 4
Network connection failed
